title: ADVENTURES OF SUPERMAN 015 (2013) (Digital) (Cypher-Empire)
description:
Adventures of Superman #15

While two boys intentionally endanger themselves in an attempt to meet Superman, Lex Luthor schemes up a way to test the limits of the Man of Steel.

Written by Kyle Killen
Art by Pia Guerra
Colored by Matthew Wilson
Cover by Yildiray Cinar

Genres: Anthology, Superhero
23 Pages
Digital Release Date: Aug 5th 2013
Age Rating: 12+ Only

------

This issue of Adventures of Superman has Pia Guerra (Eisner Award winner for Y: THE LAST MAN) drawing Superman!  :-) !!!  --STF
